fields.breakfast:
3 whole eggs + 3 egg whites scrambled with spinach, mushrooms, and tomatoes
1 slice whole-grain toast
1 small orange
fields.lunch:
150g grilled chicken breast
1 cup quinoa
1 cup steamed broccoli
1 tbsp olive oil
fields.snacks2: 1 protein shake (1 scoop whey protein, 1 cup almond milk)
fields.dinner:
200g grilled salmon
1 medium baked potato
1 cup roasted Brussels sprouts
fields.snacks3: 1 small bowl of Greek yogurt with 1 tbsp chia seeds
fields.notes: This meal plan helps maintain muscle mass while shedding fat. The moderate protein intake ensures muscle preservation, while the carbs support energy levels for workouts.

fields.breakfast:

250g grilled chicken breast
1.5 cups quinoa
1 cup steamed broccoli
1 tbsp olive oil
fields.snacks2: 1 protein shake (1.5 scoops whey protein, 1 cup almond milk)

300g grilled salmon

1 cup roasted Brussels sprouts
fields.snacks3: 1 small bowl of cottage cheese with 1 tbsp chia seeds
